CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper January 18, 1947, pg. 17, reads: "Winsome Sisters - Marverine, left, and Doris Cathcart, sisters to Mrs. Blanche Cathcart Carpenter, 'Miss Pittsburgh,' are visitors in Smoketown. The are the daughters of Mrs. Catherine Cathcart of Monroe Street. Doris is from Detroit and Marverine is a resident of St. Louis, Mo. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Sisters Marverine Cathcart and Doris Cathcart posed around floral sofa
